                   \n{370770162136537}\n\n# \u6572\u64ca\u7bc0\u594f\nTaiko Frenzy \u662f\u4e00\u6b3e\u8a2d\u5b9a\u5728\u4ee4\u4eba\u9a5a\u5606\u7684\u591a\u5f69\u5834\u666f\u4e2d\u7684\u6253\u64ca\u6a02\u7bc0\u594f\u904a\u6232\u3002\u6c89\u6d78\u5728\u53d7\u65e5\u672c\u6c11\u4fd7\u555f\u767c\u7684\u5e7b\u60f3\u4e16\u754c\u4e2d\uff0c\u4eab\u53d7\u5c08\u70ba\u904a\u6232\u5275\u4f5c\u7684\u539f\u5275\u97f3\u6a02\u3002\u63a7\u5236\u4f60\u7684\u64ca\u6253\u529b\u5ea6\uff0c\u5728\u91cd\u97f3\u62cd\u4e2d\u53d6\u5f97\u6210\u529f\uff0c\u4e26\u5b8c\u7f8e\u914d\u5408\u7bc0\u594f\uff0c\u91cb\u653e\u4ee4\u4eba\u9a5a\u5606\u7684\u6afb\u82b1\u98a8\u66b4\uff0c\u63d0\u5347\u4f60\u7684\u5f97\u5206\u4e26\u5275\u9020\u8ff7\u4eba\u7684\u8996\u89ba\u76db\u5bb4\u3002\n\n{979090080212739}\n\n# \u6309\u4f60\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u7bc0\u594f\u9032\u6b65\n\u6bcf\u9996\u539f\u5275\u66f2\u76ee\u63d0\u4f9b 4 \u500b\u96e3\u5ea6\u7d1a\u5225\uff0c\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e00\u500b\u734e\u52f5\u6027\u7684\u5b78\u7fd2\u66f2\u7dda\uff0c\u6613\u5b78\u96e3\u7cbe\uff01\u4f7f\u7528\u5404\u7a2e\u904a\u6232\u4fee\u6539\u5668\u81ea\u8a02\u6311\u6230\u3002\u722c\u4e0a\u6392\u884c\u699c\uff0c\u52aa\u529b\u89e3\u9396\u6240\u6709\u734e\u724c\uff0c\u722d\u53d6\u6210\u70ba\u7d42\u6975\u592a\u9f13\u5927\u5e2b\u3002\n\n{7698205680235034}\n\n# \u89e3\u9396\u50b3\u5947\u76ae\u819a\n\u4f60\u5728\u6b4c\u66f2\u4e2d\u7684\u9032\u6b65\u5c07\u901a\u904e\u7d93\u9a57\u503c\u548c\u6210\u5c31\u5f97\u5230\u734e\u52f5\uff0c\u89e3\u9396\u8d85\u904e 100 \u7a2e\u5316\u599d\u54c1\u3002\u6eff\u8db3\u4f60\u6536\u85cf\u5bb6\u7684\u9748\u9b42\uff0c\u5c55\u793a\u4f60\u7368\u7279\u7684\u98a8\u683c\uff01\n\n{2109860372727271}\n\n# \u5275\u4f5c\u4f60\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u6b4c\u66f2\n\u8b93\u4f60\u7684\u5275\u9020\u529b\u6d41\u6dcc\uff0c\u901a\u904e\u81ea\u8a02\u6b4c\u66f2\u529f\u80fd\u548c\u5275\u4f5c\u5de5\u5177\uff0c\u5275\u4f5c\u4e26\u6f14\u594f\u4f60\u500b\u6027\u5316\u7684\u9f13\u6a02\u5091\u4f5c\uff0c\u5c07\u4f60\u7684\u5275\u9020\u529b\u7f6e\u65bc\u805a\u5149\u71c8\u4e0b\u3002\n\n{453189640635695}\n\n\u4f60\u6e96\u5099\u597d\u8fce\u63a5\u6311\u6230\u4e86\u55ce\uff1f\u7acb\u5373\u4e0b\u8f09 Taiko Frenzy \u4e26\u901a\u904e\u6253\u9f13\u9054\u5230\u5927\u5e2b\u7d1a\u6c34\u5e73\uff01", "short_description": "\u6293\u4f4f\u9f13\u69cc\uff0c\u6572\u8d77\u7bc0\u594f\uff0c\u91cb\u653e\u4f60\u5167\u5fc3\u7684\u592a\u9f13\u5927\u5e2b\uff01"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "2503079049859049", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974868_2503079053192382_6561820935551193528_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UujB7CcFU6QQ7kNvgEJBp6s&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA2DGj-D-MwY3IInIyzRHHH8ulbjLGQlphbHSX9ch5YNA&oe=67485029"}, {"file_name": "Cover_MiniLandscape.png", "id": "1029221412172052", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75254874_1029221418838718_5450302450968066231_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IJDmqfqDWqsQ7kNvgHCyaWt&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAilRkvKDzyzhuNKm2PHaX6rgXr71stHQ9PDPafyOIRuQ&oe=67484CA6"}, {"file_name": "Cover_Landscape_en.png", "id": "997128198823994", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75280977_997128202157327_2068164725340737300_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cJCVrwEnpRsQ7kNvgEZ66_G&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA_E3Uz59eP4hZIiujs5H9jvMwaydypyVHOP2shEEnD-g&oe=674842DE"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "773548887701177", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031410_773548891034510_3149581187629526321_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=iVS8atMJru8Q7kNvgFiXE-i&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBampooG1IuT35DRGoZ2q06mEdeTlWU0JMkBIuKkkE3OQ&oe=67485998"}, {"file_name": "Cover_Portrait.png", "id": "524554866581685", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974889_524554869915018_5242899519902843975_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_PkEZwx8pBMQ7kNvgF2f2OD&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAsOMND0txKtbs5Mr3z13Xk5X_RNIFEncs5i59fNScxbA&oe=67485EAB"}, {"file_name": "CoverImageSafeAreaTemplateHero.png", "id": "520768007063344", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75282160_520768010396677_8161029491680076254_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=OO7gzQo3r40Q7kNvgFqOUw2&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB5yTXEUeWM8PADPv2fOu4djQfoEJJqzJgjONXJLofXWw&oe=67486EEC"}, {"file_name": "Cover_Square.png", "id": "493883856580584", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75363517_493883859913917_2703600091346182637_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TGX9rx9yH1QQ7kNvgEdamCM&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC8YJh6ieUrWXClSgXDLD4YLY_RXKMuC0UXLqQ9x1Lxrg&oe=674853FE"}]}, "id": "1649620848944386", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Screen5.png", "id": "693511179661100", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75340712_693511182994433_3672078632480644482_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=q7CqFzIU3CoQ7kNvgEL7Fq0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDSdJT7aJlmmJQexn45K5Lnyp63mgNgUdk6kceSExjW5g&oe=67486B57"}, {"file_name": "ScreenStore4.png", "id": "598963052430681", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031474_598963055764014_6966633497372650118_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=yPmn5mf3fyQQ7kNvgGB_vsP&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDy4_h88wtn3gfqaUJEBrMErz1Zjl5m4iJzhuAOFGtSrQ&oe=67487124"}, {"file_name": "ScreenStore1.png", "id": "709188557931825", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75203626_709188561265158_5153774901681218720_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wDMsefpb4_8Q7kNvgHGuRWl&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCKNRyHMO8DAE7Z7KsOY_84BmObEaL-9ouok2AxgWiIaw&oe=67484ABB"}, {"file_name": "ScreenStore2.png", "id": "313491285047525", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57566687_313491288380858_1744161976014076201_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rcWfofPxvQAQ7kNvgFbjuik&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA2uXgzqEDGKPLm_EX3SaVA4zaD6ztFazeHBUDFgSLuhw&oe=6748529E"}, {"file_name": "ScreenStore3.png", "id": "920322393434478", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/65395359_920322400101144_4067210821865743250_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gFUDN3Cu-1MQ7kNvgGHMhqB&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBtSMX_7zPEfe49eSToovUmTdBwlDLG-FLivgk-1dTBww&oe=67486DE9"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover_Landscape_en.png", "id": "382112371294107", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984467_382112374627440_4335625546601176072_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qifTTo7GZIsQ7kNvgGou5NO&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB14Ses_YrYyAZsJOn-tp0Fu6NNnhnRST60waR1nhHB6A&oe=674851AA"}, "display_name": "Taiko Frenzy", "keywords": ["taiko", "rhythm", "music", "japan", "drum"], "long_description": "Grab your sticks, drum up the beat and unleash your inner Taiko Master\n                                                                                                                                \n{2791919407633655}\n\n# DRUM UP THE BEAT\nTaiko Frenzy is a percussion rhythm game set in a stunning, colorful scenery. Immerse yourself in fantasy world inspired by Japanese folklore with original soundtracks exclusively composed for the game.\nControl the strength of your strikes to succeed in the accented beats and perfect your timing to the beat to unleash breathtaking sakura storms, boosting your score and creating a mesmerizing visual spectacle.\n\n{767564721869167}\n\n# PROGRESS AT YOUR OWN PACE\nEach original track offers 4 difficulty levels providing a rewarding learning curve, easy to learn, hard to master! Customize the challenge with various game modifiers.\nClimb the leaderboards and strive to unlock all the medals, aiming to become the ultimate Taiko Master.\n\n{339385065598065}\n\n# UNLOCK LEGENDARY SKINS\nYour progress in songs is rewarded with XP and achievements, unlocking over 100 cosmetics. Satisfy your collector\u2019s soul and showcase your unique style!\n\n{398008806557102}\n\n# CREATE YOUR OWN SONGS\nLet your creativity flow with the custom song feature and creation tool, enabling you to compose and play your personalized drumming masterpieces, putting your creativity in the spotlight.\n\n{1152563649212920}\n\nAre you ready to take on the challenge? Download Taiko Frenzy now and drum your way to mastery!", "short_description": "Grab your sticks, drum up the beat and unleash your inner Taiko Master!"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1519957538607535", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Taiko Frenzy", "keywords": ["taiko", "ritmo", "musica", "japon", "tambor"], "long_description": "\u00a1Agarra tus baquetas, marca el ritmo y desata tu maestro interior de Taiko!\n                                                                                                                           \n{2416053765265891}\n\n# MARCA EL RITMO\nTaiko Frenzy es un juego de ritmo de percusi\u00f3n ambientado en un escenario impresionante y colorido. Sum\u00e9rgete en un mundo de fantas\u00eda inspirado en el folclore japon\u00e9s con bandas sonoras originales compuestas exclusivamente para el juego.\nControla la fuerza de tus golpes para acertar en los ritmos acentuados y perfecciona tu sincronizaci\u00f3n con el ritmo para desatar impresionantes tormentas de sakura, aumentando tu puntuaci\u00f3n y creando un espect\u00e1culo visual asombroso.\n\n{1229017551884030}\n\n# PROGRESA A TU PROPIO RITMO\nCada pista original ofrece 4 niveles de dificultad que proporcionan una curva de aprendizaje gratificante, \u00a1f\u00e1cil de aprender, dif\u00edcil de dominar! Personaliza el desaf\u00edo con varios modificadores de juego.\nAsciende en las tablas de clasificaci\u00f3n y esfu\u00e9rzate por desbloquear todas las medallas, convertirte en el m\u00e1ximo Taiko Master.\n\n{1009701024270677}\n\n# DESBLOQUEA SKINS LEGENDARIAS\nTu progreso en las canciones se recompensa con XP y logros, desbloqueando m\u00e1s de 100 elementos cosm\u00e9ticos. \u00a1Satisface tu alma de coleccionista y muestra tu estilo \u00fanico!\n\n{2082774778791629}\n\n# CREA TUS PROPIAS CANCIONE\nDeja fluir tu creatividad con la funci\u00f3n de canciones personalizadas y la herramienta de creaci\u00f3n, que te permite componer y tocar tus propias obras maestras de percusi\u00f3n, poniendo tu creatividad en el centro de atenci\u00f3n.\n\n{407152461956006}", "short_description": "Taiko Frenzy: \u00a1Una aventura r\u00edtmica que te permite tocar al comp\u00e1s! Domina el arte de tocar el Taiko en este cautivador juego de ritmo en realidad virtual."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Cover_MiniLandscape_jp.png", "id": "3648228242055828", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982530_3648228245389161_1434821312287331495_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EoCxHEOhftcQ7kNvgGsf9wG&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBE5j4tTBgWz308_fjaOx6bjBoS8wDoPiyQSzniurj-Ow&oe=674866C5"}, {"file_name": "Cover_Portrait_jp.png", "id": "1256035242029488", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569468_1256035245362821_8632189402403459187_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_